text: Tonya Mokelki (born 10 May 1985) is a Canadian volleyball player. She is part of the Canadian women's national volleyball team. She competed at the 2009 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2009 Women's NORCECA Volleyball Championship, 2010 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2011 Pan American Games. She played for Colorado State University's women's volleyball team and SV Sinsheim. == References == Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian volleyball players
